'''热带风暴埃里卡'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Erika}}）是一场持续时间很短，只对[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]构成轻微影响的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是[[2009年大西洋飓风季|2009年大西洋飓风季]]第5场获得命名的风暴。系统源于9月1日小安的列斯群岛附近的[[东风波|东风波]]，虽然结构杂乱无章，但还是跳过热带低气压阶段，直接由气象组织归类成热带风暴并以“埃里卡”命名。当晚，气旋达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]85公里、最低[[气压|气压]]1004[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.65[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。此后不久，风暴因[[风切变|风切变]]增多而开始减弱，到9月2日时，埃里卡的强度已在热带风暴标准下限徘徊。当晚，气旋从[[瓜德罗普|瓜德罗普]]上空经过并进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]。9月3日，低气压中心同[[对流|对流]]活动完全分离，风暴随即降级成热带低气压。这天夜间，气旋退化成残留低气压，最终于9月4日在[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]附近逐渐消散。

埃里卡的强度不高，所以途经小安的列斯群岛期间引起的破坏程度很轻。瓜德罗普测得310毫米雨量，引发洪灾和[[山崩|山体滑坡]]，岛上有1万2000人失去供电。气旋退化成残留低气压前，还有另外多个岛屿测得中等程度雨量。风暴残留在波多黎各降下暴雨，最高降雨量有193毫米，在多地引发洪灾。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Erika 2009 track.png}}
8月25日，一股离开非洲西海岸的东风波行进至[[佛得角|佛得角群岛]]附近，并带有层次混乱的[[对流|对流]]活动<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | author = Daniel P. Brown | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|FL]] | date = 2009-10-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002011226/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL062009_Erika.pdf | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Storm Erika Tropical Cyclone Report | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL062009_Erika.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | author1 = Daniel Brown | author2 = Jack Beven | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-08-26 | location = Miami, FL | archivedate = 2012-09-27 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120927180015/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908261740/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908261740 | deadurl = no | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908261740/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908261740 }}</ref>。次日，东风波周围的东流在系统向西穿越大西洋期间开始呈现出组织迹象<ref>{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-27 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120927053209/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908271750/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908271750 | archivedate = 2012-09-27 | deadurl = no | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908271750/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908271750 }}</ref>。8月28日，东风波已发展出[[低气压|低气压区]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Michael Brennan | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160430032537/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908281741/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908281741 | date = 2009-08-28 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908281741/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908281741 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-04-30 }}</ref>。前方环境有利于系统进一步发展<ref>{{cite report | author1 = David Roberts | author2 = Jack Beven | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160430034246/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908282346/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908282346 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-28 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908282346/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908282346 | deadurl = no | title = Tropical weather Outlook | archivedate = 2016-04-30 }}</ref>，但低气压区的组织结构却在8月29日变得更加混乱，环流中心仅有少量对流持续<ref>{{cite report | author = Michael Brennan | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120927031014/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908291736/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908291736 | date = 2009-08-29 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908291736/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908291736 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-09-27 }}</ref>。次日，系统快速组织，中心周围逐渐发展出雨带和雷暴，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]认为低气压区很可能会在24小时内成为热带低气压<ref>{{cite report | author1 = David Roberts | deadurl = no | author2 = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-30 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | archivedate = 2012-09-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120927132452/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908301136/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908301136 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908301136/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908301136 }}</ref>。虽然对流结构理想，但系统中缺乏明确的下层环流中心，所以美国国家飓风中心此时还没有开始针对系统发布公告<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-08-31 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | archivedate = 2012-09-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120927183050/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908311803/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908311803 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200908311803/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200908311803 }}</ref>。

9月1日，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机飞入低气压区后发现闭合环流中心和热带风暴强度风速。确定有下层环流中心存在后，美国国家飓风中心将系统归类成热带风暴并以“埃里卡”（{{lang|en|Erika}}）命名，系统至此成为[[2009年大西洋飓风季|2009年大西洋飓风季]]第5场获命名的风暴。受中等强度[[风切变|风切变]]的影响，风暴结构仍略显混乱，部分中心同对流分离。但气象机构预计，由于[[海面温度|水温]]较高，埃里卡会在几天内增强成强烈热带风暴。北侧的中层[[高压脊|高压脊]]促使气旋存在期间总体保持朝西面移动。<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Eric Blake | author2 = James Franklin | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-09-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205517/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Storm Erika Discussion One | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.001.shtml? }}</ref>成为热带气旋数小时后，风暴达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时85公里，最低[[气压|气压]]1004[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.65[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度<ref name="TCR" />。不过，气象部门在当时的实际操作中是根据飓风猎人所测数据把埃里卡的最强风力时速定在95公里<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-09-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305142714/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.002.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Storm Erika Discussion Two | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.002.shtml? }}</ref>。美国国家飓风中心在风暴过后重新分析侦察机的读数，认为之前高估了埃里卡的强度<ref name="TCR" />。到了9月2日早上，气旋结构已变得非常混乱，飓风猎人的报告中称庞大的风暴内很可能存在多个环流中心<ref>{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-09-02 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Storm Erika Discussion Three | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305135437/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.003.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.003.shtml? }}</ref>。

风切变开始增多的时间早于预测模型预期，受其影响，埃里卡的强度在当天上午就降至热带风暴下限<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Eric Blake | author2 = James Franklin | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305135437/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.003.shtml | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-09-02 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Storm Erika Discussion Four | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.004.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]9月2日18:30分左右，风暴中心从[[瓜德罗普|瓜德罗普]]上空经过，此时其风速约为每小时65公里<ref name="TCR" />，然后就进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]东部<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Eric Blake | author2 = James Franklin | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-09-02 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Storm Erika Public Advisory Four-A | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305140419/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.public_a.004.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.public_a.004.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。系统环流变得长条状，并开始退化成低压槽。美国国家飓风中心认为，由于整体规模非常庞大，埃里卡的中心有可能在其它位置重组并重新增强。<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-09-02 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Storm Erika Discussion Six | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.006.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305135904/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.006.shtml }}</ref>经过短暂的对流增长，风暴强度略有回升，然后就在风切变的影响下再度减弱<ref name="TCR" />。到了9月3日下午，气旋中心已完全没有对流，美国国家飓风中心因此将之降级成热带低气压<ref>{{cite report |author=Michael Brennan |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |work=National Hurricane Center |location=Miami, FL |date=2009-09-03 |accessdate=2016-04-30 |title=Tropical Depression Erika Discussion Nine |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328064200/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.009.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.009.shtml? |archivedate=2016-03-28 }}</ref>。此后不久，美国国家飓风中心发布针对埃里卡的最后一份公告，宣布系统已消退成残留低气压区<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-09-03 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Depression Erika Discussion Ten (Final) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304213232/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.010.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al06/al062009.discus.010.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。次日，风暴残留逼近[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]南岸，令该岛普降暴雨<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Michael Brennan | author2 = David Roberts | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-09-04 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | archivedate = 2012-09-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120927133146/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200909041150/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200909041150 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200909041150/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200909041150 }}</ref>。系统最终于9月4日夜间在波多黎各以南约140公里洋面消散<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | author1 = Lixion A. Avila | author2 = Todd Kimberlain | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | date = 2009-09-04 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120927135106/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200909042332/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200909042332 | archivedate = 2012-09-27 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/200909042332/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=200909042332 }}</ref>。

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:Tropical_Storm_Erika_2009-09-03_1510Z.jpg|thumb]]
随着热带风暴埃里卡于9月1日成形，[[荷属圣马丁|荷属圣马丁]]、[[安地卡岛|安地卡岛]]、[[巴布达岛|巴布达岛]]、[[圣基茨岛|圣基茨岛]]、[[尼维斯|尼维斯]]、[[安圭拉|安圭拉]]、[[法屬聖馬丁|圣马丁岛]]和[[圣巴泰勒米|圣巴泰勒米]]均收到[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]。次日，由于气旋逼近[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]，上述所有热带风暴预警均升级成热带风暴警告。埃里卡进入加勒比海之际，[[多米尼克|多米尼克]]接获热带风暴警告，波多黎各、[[美属维尔京群岛|美属]]及[[英属维尔京群岛|英属维尔京群岛]]进入热带风暴观察预警生效状态。9月3日清晨，风暴在加勒比地区东部飘移，上述热带风暴观察预警全部升级成热带风暴警告。当晚，多米尼克和瓜德罗普的热带风暴警告停止生效，其它地区的警告均在不久后中止。<ref name="TCR" />

[[圣克洛伊岛|圣克洛伊岛]]的霍芬萨炼油厂出口原油日产量约有50万桶，但由于岛上各港口均予关闭，炼油厂也暂时停厂<ref>{{cite news | author = Haitham Haddadin | agency = [[路透社|Reuters]] | date = 2009-09-03 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Hovensa halts exports from St. Croix due to storm | archivedate = 2016-04-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160430134610/http://in.reuters.com/article/refinery-operations-hovensa-idINN039154920090903 | url = http://in.reuters.com/article/refinery-operations-hovensa-idINN039154920090903 }}</ref>。9月3日，多米尼克所有的商铺、企业都因风暴威胁而关闭。为防万一，[[安提瓜和巴布达|安提瓜和巴布达]]所有的学校和地方机场全部关闭。<ref name="Impact1">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | publisher = Caribbean 360 | date = 2009-09-03 | accessdate = 2009-09-07 | title = Erika's rains pound parts of the Eastern Caribbean; Dominica shuts down | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090907015010/http://www.caribbean360.com/News/Caribbean/Stories/2009/09/03/NEWS0000008718.html | url = http://www.caribbean360.com/News/Caribbean/Stories/2009/09/03/NEWS0000008718.html | archivedate = 2009-09-07 }}</ref>“[[嘉年华荣耀号邮轮|嘉年华荣耀号]]”（{{lang|en|Carnival Glory}}）及[[皇家加勒比国际游轮|皇家加勒比]]的另一艘邮轮推迟靠岸日期，在海上多停留1天时间，以期避开风暴<ref>{{cite news | author = Gene Sloan | publisher = ''[[今日美国|USA Today]]'' | date = 2009-09-03 | accessdate = 2009-09-05 | title = Tropical Storm Erika begins to impact cruise ships in the Caribbean | url = http://www.usatoday.com/travel/cruises/item.aspx?type=blog&ak=68498288.blog | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090905063532/http://www.usatoday.com/travel/cruises/item.aspx?type=blog&ak=68498288.blog | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2009-09-05 }}</ref>。圣马丁岛和圣巴泰勒米都进入警戒级别第2低的橙色预警状态，瓜德罗普则进入警戒级别最低的黄色预警状态<ref>{{cite report | author = Meteo-France | publisher = Government of Guadeloupe | date = 2009-09-02 | title = Tempête tropicale Erika}}</ref>。波多黎各政府官员于9月4日关闭学校和政府办事处，并在岛上各地开设共433个避难所。多米尼加共和国政府向9个省发布警告，以防万一。附近的[[海地|海地]]也发出气旋可能产生暴雨的警报。<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = ''El Universal'' | date = 2009-09-03 | accessdate = 2011-07-25 | title = Erika se debilita a depresión tropical en ruta a Puerto Rico | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110725001217/http://internacional.eluniversal.com/2009/09/03/int_ava_erika-se-debilita-a_03A2698971.shtml | url = http://internacional.eluniversal.com/2009/09/03/int_ava_erika-se-debilita-a_03A2698971.shtml | archivedate = 2011-07-25 }}</ref>

== 影响 ==
[[File:Erika_2009_rainfall.gif|thumb]]
9月3日，受埃里卡产生暴雨引发的洪灾影响，多米尼克所有政府建筑暂时关闭<ref name="Impact1" />。据报导，小萨凡纳发生[[山崩|山体滑坡]]，导致道路封闭<ref>{{cite news |author=Edona Jno Baptistse |publisher=''Dominica News Online'' |date=2009-09-04 |accessdate=2009-09-04 |title=Minister thankful Dominica was spared from Erika (Photos included) |url=http://www.dominicanewsonline.com/all_news/general/7179.html |archivedate=2009-09-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5jXy6Z3IW?url=http://www.dominicanewsonline.com/all_news/general/7179.html }}</ref>。气旋在瓜德罗普产生暴雨，多地降雨量超过200毫米，局部地区因此爆发洪灾<ref name="AFP1" />。[[拉代西拉德岛|拉代西拉德岛]]的降雨量最高，达310毫米，还以240毫米刷新24小时降雨量纪录<ref name="Meteo-FranceTCR">{{cite web | author1 = Christophe Montout | author2 = Roland Mazurie | publisher = Météo-France | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tempête tropicale Erika: Passage en Guadeloupe les 2 et 3 septembre 2009 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304031714/http://www.meteo.fr/temps/domtom/antilles/pack-public/alaune/cr_erika.pdf | url = http://www.meteo.fr/temps/domtom/antilles/pack-public/alaune/cr_erika.pdf | format = PDF | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[玛丽-加朗特岛|玛丽-加朗特岛]]测得每小时90公里的持续风速，[[布扬特_(瓜德罗普)|布扬特]]（{{lang|en|Bouillante}}）还发生岩崩<ref name="AFP1">{{cite news |author=AFP, France Antilles |publisher=Catastrophes Naturalles |date=2009-09-03 |accessdate=2009-09-04 |title=07 - La tempête tropicale Erika affecte la Guadeloupe |archivedate=2009-09-04 |url=http://www.catnat.net/actualites/catastrophes-france/9841-07-la-tempete-tropicale-erika-affecte-la-guadeloupe |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5jXzWDAt3?url=http://www.catnat.net/actualites/catastrophes-france/9841-07-la-tempete-tropicale-erika-affecte-la-guadeloupe }}</ref>。洪水令多条道路无数通行。风暴期间，估计岛上共有1万2000人失去供电<ref name="Rainfall">{{cite news | author = Meteo-France | publisher = ''France Antilles'' | date = 2009-09-03 | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Erika : beaucoup d'eau mais peu de dégats | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303202515/http://www.martinique.franceantilles.fr/actualite/faitsdivers/erika-beaucoup-d-eau-mais-peu-de-degats-03-09-2009-43458.php | url = http://www.martinique.franceantilles.fr/actualite/faitsdivers/erika-beaucoup-d-eau-mais-peu-de-degats-03-09-2009-43458.php }}</ref>。[[特立尼达岛|特立尼达岛]]山麓沿线的降雨量达到140毫米，圣马丁岛的最高降雨量也有94毫米<ref name="Rainfall" />。美属维尔京群岛的24小时降雨量为41毫米<ref>{{cite report |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |year=2010 |accessdate=2010-09-02 |title=St. Croix Event Report: Heavy Rain |archivedate=2010-09-02 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~784789 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5sRanBmSm?url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~784789 |date= }}</ref>，引发轻度洪灾<ref>{{cite report |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |year=2010 |accessdate=2010-09-02 |title=St. Thomas Event Report: Flash Flood |archivedate=2010-09-02 |url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~784791 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5sRap2rJ6?url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~784791 |date= }}</ref>。

埃里卡的残留在波多黎各产生大量降水，致使包括拉普拉达河、洛伊萨河在内的多条河流泛滥，引起大规模洪灾<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Writer |publisher=Diario Digital RD |date=2009-09-06 |accessdate=2011-10-02 |title=Erika empapa a Puerto Rico y parte de Dominicana |url=http://www.diariodigital.com.do/articulo,44737,html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111002091014/http://www.diariodigital.com.do/articulo%2C44737%2Chtml |archivedate=2011-10-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[纳瓜沃|纳瓜沃]]有气象站测得201毫米雨量<ref name=HPC>{{cite report | author = Hydrometorological Prediction Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2009-09-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225554/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/erika2009.html | accessdate = 2016-04-30 | title = Tropical Depression Erika - September 3–5, 2009 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/erika2009.html }}</ref><ref name="NWS">{{cite report |author=National Weather Service in San Juan, Puerto Rico |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |date=2009-09-06 |accessdate=2009-09-06 |title=Preliminary Rainfall Totals From Remnants of Tropical Depression Erika in Puerto Rico |url=http://www.srh.noaa.gov/productview.php?pil=PNSSJU&version=0 |archivedate=2009-09-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5jacSbj9D?url=http://www.srh.noaa.gov/productview.php?pil=PNSSJU }}</ref>。另有多地测得的降雨量在100毫米以上<ref name="NWS" />。[[瓜尼卡|瓜尼卡]]有多户民宅被淹，经济损失约为5000美元<ref>{{cite report |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |year=2010 |accessdate=2010-09-02 |title=Puerto Rico Event Report: Flash Flood |url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~785715 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5sRazCdpw?url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~785715 |archivedate=2010-09-02 |deadurl=yes |date= }}</ref>。[[拉斯彼德拉斯_(波多黎各)|拉斯彼德拉斯]]的受灾程度最重，洪灾导致的损失数额约为1万5000美元<ref>{{cite report |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |year=2010 |accessdate=2010-09-02 |title=Puerto Rico Event Report: Flash Flood |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5sRb1KnLy?url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~785238 |archivedate=2010-09-02 |url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~785238 |date= }}</ref>。岛上还有河流水位上涨到8.92米，比洪水水位还高2.22米<ref>{{cite report |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |year=2010 |accessdate=2010-09-02 |title=Puerto Rico Event Report: Flash Flood |archivedate=2010-09-02 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~785435 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5sRb6T3eR?url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~785435 |date= }}</ref>。[[法哈多|法哈多]]有多户民居被洪水淹没，估计损失数额约有1万美元<ref>{{cite report |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |year=2009 |accessdate=2010-09-02 |title=Puerto Rico Event Report: Flash Flood |url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~785732 |archivedate=2010-09-02 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5sRb80Tw1?url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~785732 |deadurl=yes |date= }}</ref>。此外，[[卡瓜斯|卡瓜斯]]也因洪灾蒙受了价值5000美元的破坏<ref>{{cite report |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |year=2010 |accessdate=2010-09-02 |title=Puerto Rico Event Report: Flash Flood |url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~785901 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5sRawg3NG?url=http://www4.ncdc.noaa.gov/cgi-win/wwcgi.dll?wwevent~ShowEvent~785901 |archivedate=2010-09-02 |date= }}</ref>。面对持续性的降水和洪灾威胁，多米尼加共和国向[[圣母省|圣母省]]、[[赛堡省|赛堡省]]、[[阿托马约省|阿托马约省]]、[[银山省|银山省]]、[[山美纳省|山美纳省]]、[[杜华德省|杜华德省]]和[[玛丽亚·桑其斯省|玛丽亚·桑其斯省]]发布洪灾警报<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = ''Antena en Linea'' | date = 2009-09-04 | title = Alerta contra inundaciones en siete provincias por Erika}}</ref>。
